{"tid":2401760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"16歲學生去年襲警原判感化 律政司向上訴庭覆核得直 將改判更生或勞教","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:05:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"298392bb03d841dae8a4fe069997d96c543c8558","tid":2401760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13584&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=17b734a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13584</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭  <br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官<br />\n#陳慶偉法官<br />\n#刑期覆核<br />\n#20200119旺角<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n陳<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2020年1月19日在旺角登打士街43A號外襲擊警員X。據悉，答辯人企圖以磚頭投擲警員。認罪後，嚴舜儀主任裁判官判處答辯人12個月感化令。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n申請人（律政司司長）<br />\n陳詞認為原審裁判官原則上犯錯及量刑明顯過輕，原審裁判官偏離一般襲警判刑原則，而且答辯人沒有例外情況，答辯人亦沒良好背景作為減刑因素<br />\n<br />\n答辯人當時與約100名示威者集結，他的行為有機會鼓動現場示威人士，原審裁判官忽視了這個加刑因素<br />\n<br />\n雖然答辯人指自己沒有意圖向警方投擲磚頭，但申請人指事實上，答辯人手持磚頭，已將意圖付諸行動，陳慶偉法官留意到磚頭的邊緣很鋒利。申請人引用案例指即使襲警時沒有使用武器，一般都是處以禁閉式刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長訴SHY案指出感化令只是側重於更生，阻嚇性及懲罰性不足，潘兆初高等法院首席法官留意到感化官指答辯人態度迴避，一開始並不承認錯，質疑原審裁判官沒有適當地處理感化官的觀察，沒有解釋如何以感化令協助答辯人更生<br />\n<br />\n（未完...待續）<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n上訴庭批准司長覆核申請，認為原審裁判官原則上犯錯及量刑明顯過輕，上訴庭認為原審裁判官沒有顧及阻嚇性及懲罰性，偏離了此類案件的一般量刑原則。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭下令期間為答辯人索取勞教中心及更生中心報告，押後至2021年3月3日判刑"},{"pid":"1e531447035ecf4d207143d05440493e865f853b","tid":2401760,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"538081474f05ee2870a6c7987125a2113d5f7c3e","tid":2401760,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"0de9c90690d3e4fc73103ec2999e69c5c0fa21f4","tid":2401760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e531447035ecf4d207143d05440493e865f853b","tid":2401760,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c289c30778e44b667a982a1b2349711fc61cb68c","tid":2401760,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"上訴庭=納粹法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741f20793c91058822e08cb80ba18864b3d3a2a8","tid":2401760,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"嚴官第一次比人覆核？"},{"pid":"0260ceba1643b6bff43a3c9b9c679086c80cf20f","tid":2401760,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"741f20793c91058822e08cb80ba18864b3d3a2a8","tid":2401760,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"嚴官第一次比人覆核？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"係 連佢出名釘都覆核⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743c7ad5a36ac9c96485e84e1033f1f0d0c8e612","tid":2401760,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c289c30778e44b667a982a1b2349711fc61cb68c","tid":2401760,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"上訴庭=納粹法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:47:23.000Z","msg":"加刑庭"},{"pid":"3a3c0d47e5e5a3e4324faf498f323668b05aa87c","tid":2401760,"uid"